<li id="cite_note-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-3" title="">^</a></b> In practice, each prefabricated element, destined to be assembled into a cylinder, corresponds to an explosive device surrounded by two discs, which explains why the line of disks is terminated at each end by a hollow half module.</li>
</ol>
